@startuml
title Athena JS CLI bootstrap (after hardening)

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam Rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #DAF7DC
  BorderColor #3C8D40
}
skinparam ArrowColor #4E6A8A

actor "Developer" as Dev

rectangle "bin/athena-js.js" as Bin #C6EFCE
rectangle "dist/cli/index.js exists?" as Exists #D9EAF7
rectangle "Import and run\nrunCLI(argv)" as RunCli #B7DEE8
rectangle "Friendly recovery message\n(version + reinstall command)" as Recovery #FCE4D6

Dev --> Bin : run `athena-js`
Bin --> Exists : check generated bundle path
Exists --> RunCli : yes
Exists --> Recovery : no
Recovery --> Dev : actionable fix path

note right of Recovery
Includes expected file path and installed version.
Avoids opaque ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND-only output.
end note

@enduml
